Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:43.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:48.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:52.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:01.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:11.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:20.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:30.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:39.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:46.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:55.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:43.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:48.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:52.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:01.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:11.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:20.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:30.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:39.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:46.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:55.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:33.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:38.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:42.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:02.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:14.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:19.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:28.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:32.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:44.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:49.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
